      </p>
        <button class="btn-primary fw-bold border-white bg-white" style=" margin-bottom: 33px;"><a href="/register" style="color: aliceblue; text-decoration: none;">Register</a></button>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p> Project for <a href="https://stige.tech/" class="text-white">StigeTask</a></p>
  </footer>
  </body>
</html>
